OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1784918934
OL,3,CJersey 'not on track' to meet 2030
OL,4,Ccarbon emissions target
OL,6,FJersey must do more to meet its
OL,7,Femissions targets, campaigners say in
OL,8,Flight of a new report that shows the
OL,9,Fisland is not on track with its
OL,10,Fclimate targets.
OL,12,FJersey's Greenhouse Gas Emissions
OL,13,Fstatistics show that the island's
OL,14,Femissions have fallen by 49% since
OL,15,F1990.
OL,17,FHowever, Jersey must reduce its
OL,18,Femissions by 68% in the next four
OL,19,Fyears to meet its Paris Agreement
OL,20,Ftarget.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
