PN,35202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1784918934
OL,3,CJersey 'not on track' to meet 2030
OL,4,Ccarbon emissions target
OL,6,FSenator Mary Le Hegarat, Jersey's
OL,7,FMinister for the Environment, says
OL,8,Fthat while emissions have continued to
OL,9,Ffall, Jersey is "not currently on
OL,10,Ftrack to meet its interim 2030
OL,11,Femissions reduction target".
OL,13,FHowever, the Minister maintains that
OL,14,Fachieving net zero by 2050 is still
OL,15,Fpossible.
OL,17,FJersey's emissions have fallen by 49%
OL,18,Fsince 1990, putting it behind both
OL,19,FGuernsey and the UK:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1784918934
OL,3,CJersey 'not on track' to meet 2030
OL,4,Ccarbon emissions target
OL,6,FThe report has prompted concerns that
OL,7,Fthe government needs to act quickly,
OL,8,Fas emissions only dropped by 1% in the
OL,9,Fyear to 2024.
OL,11,FNigel Jones, an environmentalist and
OL,12,FChair of Jersey in Transition, says
OL,13,Fthat the government must provide more
OL,14,Feffective and clear leadership.
OL,16,F"It's clear that we're not really
OL,17,Fmaking enough progress to get to our
OL,18,F2035 target," Nigel told ITV News.
OL,19,F"We're certainly not going to get ot
OL,20,Fthe 2050 target at this rate.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1784918934
OL,3,CJersey 'not on track' to meet 2030
OL,4,Ccarbon emissions target
OL,6,F"I'd like to see a stronger, clearer
OL,7,Fmessage from the government to say
OL,8,Fthis is not a bad thing - this is a
OL,9,Fgood thing - this is an investment in
OL,10,Four future.
OL,12,F"We're going to get increased health,
OL,13,Fwe're going to get clearer air, and
OL,14,Fwe're going to get a better reputation
OL,15,Finternationally.
OL,17,F"If the message from the government
OL,18,Fcould clearly say that and say it
OL,19,Fconsistently, I think we'd all be able
OL,20,Fto come along much better."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1784918934
OL,3,CJersey 'not on track' to meet 2030
OL,4,Ccarbon emissions target
OL,6,FIn a statement, the Environment
OL,7,FMinister maintains that achieving net
OL,8,Fzero by 2050 "remains both feasible
OL,9,Fand affordable".
OL,11,F"The Climate Council's report,
OL,12,Fpublished in March 2026, makes clear
OL,13,Fthat Jersey is not currently on track
OL,14,Fto meet its interim 2030 emissions
OL,15,Freduction target," Senator Le Hegarat
OL,16,Fstates.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
