FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1784918934
OL,3,CJersey 'not on track' to meet 2030
OL,4,Ccarbon emissions target
OL,6,F"Over this term of Government, I will
OL,7,Fcontinue to work on the delivery of
OL,8,Fthe Carbon Neutral Roadmap, adapting
OL,9,Fits implementation in line with our
OL,10,Fpriorities and available resources.
OL,12,F"The Carbon Neutral Roadmap remains
OL,13,Four long-term framework for reducing
OL,14,Femissions and meeting Jersey's
OL,15,Fcommitments under the Paris Agreement.
OL,17,F"While challenges remain, we will
OL,18,Fcontinue to take a pragmatic and
OL,19,Faffordable approach to delivering the
OL,20,Ftransition to net zero."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/6
